{"tid":51424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"官方：奧斯卡加盟上海上港","createTime":"2016-12-23T08:09:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-03T06:36:04.000Z","uid":60712,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8542f25d42fdbf2f8427d14c12c4069789fdd2","tid":51424,"uid":60712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"官方：奧斯卡加盟上海上港<br />\n<br />\n上海上港俱樂部宣佈，此前效力車路士的巴西球星奧斯卡正式加盟球隊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t689ljn2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft689ljn2&h=49c208cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a865f1bc8d9d97d1c2ee9875741b555439754db","tid":51424,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"魔性澎湃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n摩佬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e806b4392a1edb654a90abb653a3851ac9a52b84","tid":51424,"uid":60712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"上海上港集團足球俱樂部：上海上港集團足球俱樂部與切爾西足球俱樂部已正式完成關於巴西球員奧斯卡的轉會協議。奧斯卡將於近日抵達上海，正式加盟上海上港。在效力於切爾西的4年時間裡，奧斯卡在各項賽事中為球隊出場203次，打進38球，並與球隊一起獲得了一座英超聯賽的冠軍、一座歐聯盃的冠軍和一座聯賽杯的冠軍。"},{"pid":"2b15fef893aa89421dd972b3ace715b95d54543b","tid":51424,"uid":60712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:11:09.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 25歲過中超<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e8adfe03390ceb27b6da3b3965a9aef4db9bff","tid":51424,"uid":52423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:11:23.000Z","msg":"當年既超新星，當打年齡淪落到去中超<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問佢同古天奴比邊但勁啲?"},{"pid":"3a773cf5f453b22d9fc35faf2edcb977d61612f4","tid":51424,"uid":607